Class ItemNode<T>

  • java.lang.Object

  • Type Parameters:
    T - generic parameter to declare the type of this node
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CollectionNode, DataNode

    public abstract class ItemNode<T>
extends Node<T>
implements Iterable
    An ItemNode is a Node which is created within the PubSub-tree (on the XMPP-server). Therefore it needs to implement the de.tudresden.inf.rn.mobilis.sea.pubsub.model.tree.utils.Iterable interface (so a de.tudresden.inf.rn.mobilis.sea.pubsub.model.tree.utils.Iterator may visit this node)
